{"tid":2353865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會委員會疑擴至以ZOOM開正式會議","createTime":"2021-01-05T05:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T05:49:05.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"899f48b0ea905bb2edd255a0f70223dac78ae211","tid":2353865,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"立法會議事規則委員會明日召開特別會議，疑將Zoom視像開會擴展至事務委員會、法案委員會和小組委員會正式會議。非建制派議員鄭松泰表明反對，質疑ZOOM開會的做法違反《議事規則》，批今次修改是以防疫為由的政治打壓，日後若然出現防疫以外的緊急情況，如有市民因為惡法包圍立法會，議員都可以在外用ZOOM開會逃避民意，斥「極權以防疫為名，用盡所有方式摧毀立法會嘅制度、一致性同習慣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/JSL7FB3D6ZDPHBO4CCZII4KSQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FJSL7FB3D6ZDPHBO4CCZII4KSQU%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOY093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=c5213560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FJSL7FB3D6ZDPHBO4CCZII4KSQU%2F&h=51f5c9ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/JSL7FB3D6ZDPHBO4CCZII4KSQU/</a>"},{"pid":"adf77ec61d6502b83a5d649b22840b18b80cc5c5","tid":2353865,"uid":276525,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"執7咗佢啦<br />\n連去現場瞓都唔使"},{"pid":"c793611e3e711dffd1a39035abb6adca493da089","tid":2353865,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"hack 入去播 av"},{"pid":"72b969ceac9744e21a6f9ce12647d21a53b835af","tid":2353865,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦,佢地玩壞晒架啦"},{"pid":"9fa37f61447a9f27d40ac4f06afe27d7303b649e","tid":2353865,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915277d72aa18adbe9090850165df02dd0ba6753","tid":2353865,"uid":335434,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":